# Buidls
*.apk
*.aab

# Understand-Anything knowledge graph: the graph itself is COMMITTED (per the
# plugin's team model — "commit it once, teammates skip the pipeline"), so
# contributors can browse it locally via `pnpm graph` without burning tokens.
# Only scratch/working dirs are ignored. Refresh: /understand (maintainer).
.understand-anything/intermediate/
.understand-anything/tmp/
.understand-anything/.trash-*
